data.description: Welcome to your next home in Cape Coral! This single-family home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage, large driveway with 3 car extension providing ample space. Brand New Roof (2023) and New Electrical Panel (2023). Perfect for your first home or an investment property. Situated in a great location, you'll have easy access to all the amenities Cape Coral has to offer, including shopping, dining, and entertainment options. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautiful tile flooring. The vaulted ceilings create an open and airy atmosphere, adding to the overall charm of this home. You will love the spacious master bedroom with a walk-in closet. The split floor plan offers privacy and convenience, making it perfect for those who love to entertain. The backyard is large with landscaping on the property line giving you plenty of privacy. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a beautiful single-family home in Cape Coral!
